data.title: Hookah to B Site Tube Rendezvous
data.description: Enable yourself to play in Hookah and trade utility early into the round with this simple setup.

data.title: A Site Rendezvous for U-Hall + A Main Hold
data.description: This Rendezvous can be used to play however you want from / in front of U-Hall to hold A Main or U-Hall and then safely teleport out after taking an engagement or facing enemy utility.
